  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REACH THE PEAK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull yourself up a treacherous mountain to reach the legendary <strong>Peak</strong><i>, </i>where eternal glory and a wonderful gift awaits. This journey demands complete mastery in the legendary art of climbing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Game includes one free expansion</u></strong>, a completely new, bigger adventure featuring a full second chapter that’s more brutal, more ambitious, and absolutely not easier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/e5e8b71f84899f01771065639b0f95c2.poster.avif?t=1766018522\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/e5e8b71f84899f01771065639b0f95c2.webm?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/e5e8b71f84899f01771065639b0f95c2.mp4?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No deaths or violence.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Just the constant fear of falling and losing all your progress. Perhaps that is worse…</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics based climbing</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Use only your mouse to control the arms of the climber. Gamepad supported.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless suffering.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The world record is under 4 minutes. You, however, will be here for hours. Possibly forever.</i></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>But not:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legs... You cannot use your legs for some reason.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/d9127771d719f6e49624631b00b61e4a.poster.avif?t=1766018522\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/d9127771d719f6e49624631b00b61e4a.webm?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/d9127771d719f6e49624631b00b61e4a.mp4?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FAILURE IS A TEACHER. EACH FALL IS A LESSON.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a philosophical journey, uncover lessons of ancient wisdom and who knows... perhaps even the meaning of life itself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/923b995d9469cabbcae0936a5ed64fe2.poster.avif?t=1766018522\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/923b995d9469cabbcae0936a5ed64fe2.webm?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/923b995d9469cabbcae0936a5ed64fe2.mp4?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ETERNAL GLORY AWAITS YOU AT THE PEAK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer each of the 7 uniquely designed areas that make up this one colossal mountain to receive the grand prize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expansion - Chapter 2:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new, bigger adventure featuring a full second chapter that’s more brutal, more ambitious, and absolutely not easier. Adds 9 completely new zones and is included with the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/52b778636b26b843a937686d29702219.poster.avif?t=1766018522\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/52b778636b26b843a937686d29702219.webm?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/52b778636b26b843a937686d29702219.mp4?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“The ascent has become familiar… almost comforting. But alas, far below, within the endless water that binds earth to heaven, lies a glimmer of hope - and perhaps a deeper truth.”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note from the developer:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is inspired by \"Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy\", itself a homage to an older game made by Jazzuo. I aimed to capture the magic of GOI's intensely difficult gameplay, which becomes comically easy once you master it.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REACH THE PEAK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull yourself up a treacherous mountain to reach the legendary <strong>Peak</strong><i>, </i>where eternal glory and a wonderful gift awaits. This journey demands complete mastery in the legendary art of climbing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Game includes one free expansion</u></strong>, a completely new, bigger adventure featuring a full second chapter that’s more brutal, more ambitious, and absolutely not easier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/e5e8b71f84899f01771065639b0f95c2.poster.avif?t=1766018522\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/e5e8b71f84899f01771065639b0f95c2.webm?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/e5e8b71f84899f01771065639b0f95c2.mp4?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No deaths or violence.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Just the constant fear of falling and losing all your progress. Perhaps that is worse…</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics based climbing</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Use only your mouse to control the arms of the climber. Gamepad supported.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless suffering.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The world record is under 4 minutes. You, however, will be here for hours. Possibly forever.</i></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>But not