e up this one colossal mountain to receive the grand prize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expansion - Chapter 2:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new, bigger adventure featuring a full second chapter that’s more brutal, more ambitious, and absolutely not easier. Adds 9 completely new zones and is included with the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/52b778636b26b843a937686d29702219.poster.avif?t=1766018522\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/52b778636b26b843a937686d29702219.webm?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497920/extras/52b778636b26b843a937686d29702219.mp4?t=1766018522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“The ascent has become familiar… almost comforting. But alas, far below, within the endless water that binds earth to heaven, lies a glimmer of hope - and perhaps a deeper truth.”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note from the developer:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is inspired by \"Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy\", itself a homage to an older game made by Jazzuo. I aimed to capture the magic of GOI's intensely difficult gameplay, which becomes comically easy once you master it.</p>",
